                                Jenkins Runner


DESCRIPTION

Run jobs and wait until they finish. This is mainly a little utility script
for my Makefiles.


ENV VARS

JENKINS_USERNAME - Your Jenkins username
JENKINS_PASSWORD - Your Jenkins password
JENKINS_URL      - The URL for the Jenkins server
JENKINS_VERIFY   - SSL verification (blank = true, false = false, or path to cert)


EXAMPLES

Without Params:

export JENKINS_URL = "https://foo" ./jenkins-runner run myjob

With Params:

export JENKINS_URL = "https://foo" ./jenkins-runner run myjob '{"BRANCH": "master"}'

View Other Commands:

./jenkins-runner help
